a4d5f27617f6f679c8b1d5","tid":2012830,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T04:14:04.000Z","msg":"琴日審訊重點：<br />\n<br />\n代表控方的資深大律師郭棟明先作出開案陳詞。郭首先簡述《公案條例》關於公眾集會及遊行的條文，指出任何50人以上公眾集會及30人以上遊行均須向警方申請，而警方有權阻止、停止及解散任何未經批准的集結。<br />\n<br />\n控方則根據閉路電視片段攝得他們的逃跑路線、<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">三人的裝備、逃離現場的時空及逃避警方的行為，以及少女在現場的招認等，認為三人身處現場是鼓勵及有意圖鼓勵他人干犯暴動。<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n郭補充，若暴動罪未能成立，法庭應考慮較輕的交替控罪，即非法集結罪。他又要求法庭考慮裁定事件是否暴動、暴動何時開始、及三人是在何時參與集結。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1073295\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1073295&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HeBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=120189f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1073295&h=a8fd00f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1073295</a>"},{"pid":"0aff2acfda464571ee37cfe35cef120632d109a8","tid":2012830,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T04:17:41.000Z","msg":"#區域法院第卅八庭<br />\n#郭啟安法官 #審訊 [2/10]<br />\n#0728上環 #暴動<br />\n<br />\n1213 傳召證人PW2：陳總警司"},{"pid":"2db5256255e6f95bd12552940a38389e63465721","tid":2012830,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T04:24:11.000Z","msg":"有陪審團？希望係自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc22fe74830eef8b456c8c631059ca768074fbe5","tid":2012830,"uid":16374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T04:24:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔該"},{"pid":"002cafd11ffe47bc8d213d724ee3108cc46a750c","tid":2012830,"uid":16374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2db5256255e6f95bd12552940a38389e63465721","tid":2012830,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T04:24:11.000Z","msg":"有陪審團？希望係自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\